OL,3,CPremier League clubs face tax hikes
OL,4,Cafter stadiums hit in Budget
OL,6,FPremier League football clubs are set
OL,7,Fto face sharp rises in the taxes on
OL,8,Ftheir stadiums next year, with Arsenal
OL,9,Fand Manchester United among those
OL,10,Ffacing much higher bills.
OL,12,FAnalysis of official Government data
OL,13,Fhas revealed a significant increase in
OL,14,Fthe valuations of the biggest football
OL,15,Fvenues in England and Wales.
