OL,3,CPremier League clubs face tax hikes
OL,4,Cafter stadiums hit in Budget
OL,6,FGlobal tax firm Ryan's analysis of
OL,7,FValuation Office Agency (VOA) data
OL,8,Ffound that the rateable values of
OL,9,Fstadiums across the top five English
OL,10,Fdivisions have jumped by 25% to
OL,11,F#111.74 million.
OL,13,FIn the Budget last week, the
OL,14,FGovernment confirmed that new business
OL,15,Frates payments for commercial
OL,16,Fproperties would be based on
OL,17,Fvaluations made in 2024 and a new
OL,18,Freduced multiplier to calculate their
OL,19,Foverall bills.
