OL,3,CPremier League clubs face tax hikes
OL,4,Cafter stadiums hit in Budget
OL,6,FThis will result in higher payments
OL,7,Ffor most clubs from next year, with
OL,8,Ffurther increases in following years
OL,9,Fas transitional relief caps fade away.
OL,11,FArsenal will face the largest cash
OL,12,Fincrease of all Premier League clubs,
OL,13,Fwith the analysis showing they are set
OL,14,Fto see their rates bill rise by #1.1
OL,15,Fmillion to #4.8 million for the year
OL,16,Ffrom April, after the valuation of the
OL,17,Fstadium rose to #11 million.
