OL,3,CPremier League clubs face tax hikes
OL,4,Cafter stadiums hit in Budget
OL,6,FElsewhere, Manchester United will see
OL,7,Fthe rates bill for Old Trafford jump
OL,8,Fby #973,840 from April to #5.79
OL,9,Fmillion.
OL,11,FThe Tottenham Hotspur Stadium will
OL,12,Fonly get a #96,200 rise but it will
OL,13,Fstill have the largest bill in the
OL,14,Fdivision for its stadium, at #5.8
OL,15,Fmillion.
