OL,3,CPremier League clubs face tax hikes
OL,4,Cafter stadiums hit in Budget
OL,6,FOther stadiums have seen sharp rises
OL,7,Fin their rateable values, such as
OL,8,FBrentford's GTech Stadium, which has
OL,9,Fseen its value jump by 300%, and
OL,10,FNottingham Forest's City Ground which
OL,11,Fhas recorded a 153.4% rise in its
OL,12,Fvalue.
OL,14,FWithin the Premier League, Wolves and
OL,15,FBurnley were the only clubs to see
OL,16,Fvaluations fall, dipping by 32.8% and
OL,17,F6.3% respectively.
