OL,3,CPremier League clubs face tax hikes
OL,4,Cafter stadiums hit in Budget
OL,6,FElsewhere, Sheffield Wednesday's
OL,7,Fstadium valuation still rose 21.8%
OL,8,Fdespite the club being in
OL,9,Fadministration.
OL,11,FFellow Championship side Wrexham
OL,12,Frecorded the largest increase in
OL,13,FEngland and Wales, with its Racecourse
OL,14,FGround valuation soaring 612.4%.
