OL,3,CPremier League clubs face tax hikes
OL,4,Cafter stadiums hit in Budget
OL,6,FAlex Probyn, practice leader for
OL,7,FEurope and Asia-Pacific property tax
OL,8,Fat Ryan, said: "Football stadiums are
OL,9,Fvalued using the receipts and
OL,10,Fexpenditure method, which is driven
OL,11,Fentirely by income and operating
OL,12,Fperformance.
OL,14,F"The last revaluation was based on
OL,15,FApril 1 2021, when grounds were still
OL,16,Fshut with full-capacity crowds not
OL,17,Freturning until July 2021.
